{
  "text": "Preparation of ras-transformed and control C3H 10T1/2 fibroblasts. Using the calcium phosphate method, C3H 10T1/2 murine fibroblasts were transfected with either the eukaryotic expression vector pRC/RSV (Invitrogen) or pRC/RSV containing the v-Ha-ras oncogene [CITATION_1] . Stable transfectants were isolated by selection in G418 (400 g/ml), and cell transformation was confirmed by morphology and focus-forming ability.",
